{"id": "otel-sa-003", "category": "otel_single_agent", "difficulty": "medium", "query": "checkout 服务最近 30 分钟的 trace 里有没有错误？同时查一下对应的 error rate 指标，帮我做交叉验证。", "expected_skills": ["otel-query"], "expected_intent": "troubleshoot", "expected_metrics": ["error_rate"], "expected_entities": ["checkout"], "expected_tool_calls": [{"tool": "query_traces", "args_contains": {"service": "checkout", "lookback": "30m"}}, {"tool": "query_metrics", "args_contains": {"query": "error"}}], "expected_answer_contains": ["trace", "error", "metric", "checkout"]}
{"id": "otel-sa-004", "category": "otel_single_agent", "difficulty": "medium", "query": "用 Jaeger 查一下 cart 服务中所有 duration 超过 500ms 的慢 trace，按 span 耗时排序。", "expected_skills": ["otel-query"], "expected_intent": "troubleshoot", "expected_metrics": [], "expected_entities": ["cart", "jaeger"], "expected_tool_calls": [{"tool": "query_traces", "args_contains": {"service": "cart", "min_duration_ms": 500}}], "expected_answer_contains": ["slow", "trace", "duration", "cart", "500ms"]}
{"id": "otel-sa-005", "category": "otel_single_agent", "difficulty": "medium", "query": "Prometheus 里查一下 adservice 的 gRPC 调用成功率，以及 GetAds 接口的 p99 延迟，看看有没有性能退化。", "expected_skills": ["otel-query"], "expected_intent": "metrics", "expected_metrics": ["p99"], "expected_entities": ["adservice", "grpc", "getads"], "expected_tool_calls": [{"tool": "query_metrics", "args_contains": {"query": "rpc_server"}}], "expected_answer_contains": ["gRPC", "success_rate", "p99", "adservice", "GetAds"]}
{"id": "otel-sa-006", "category": "otel_single_agent", "difficulty": "hard", "query": "前端 /api/checkout 接口的 trace 显示 downstream 调用链路过长，帮我从 Jaeger 拉取完整 trace 树，分析每个 span 的耗时占比，找出瓶颈节点。", "expected_skills": ["otel-query"], "expected_intent": "troubleshoot", "expected_metrics": ["p95"], "expected_entities": ["checkout", "jaeger", "span"], "expected_tool_calls": [{"tool": "query_traces", "args_contains": {"service": "checkout"}}], "expected_answer_contains": ["trace", "span", "bottleneck", "checkout", "waterfall", "duration"]}
